# Galaxy Pong

Welcome to the GitHub repository for **Galaxy Pong** ‚Äì a space-themed Pong clone with retro assets, built using the Unity Game Engine. This simple yet engaging game features two exciting game modes: versus player and versus AI, with three difficulty levels for AI opponents.

## Features

- **Game Modes:**
  - *Versus Player:* Challenge your friend in a classic head-to-head Pong match.
  - *Versus AI:* Test your skills against AI opponents with three difficulty levels.

- **Controls:**
  - *Player 1 (Web):* Left arrow, Right arrow keys.
  - *Player 2 (Web):* A, D keys.
  - *Mobile (Player 1):* Touch the lower half of the screen to control.
  - *Mobile (Player 2):* Touch the upper half of the screen to control.

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository to your local machine. 
```bash
git clone https://github.com/MarcioMed07/Galaxy-Pong.git
```
2. Open the project in Unity.

3. Run the game in the Unity editor or build it for the web to enjoy the space-themed Pong experience.

## Play Now

The game is available for free on [itch.io](https://marciomed07.itch.io/galaxy-pong). Give it a try and experience the cosmic thrill!

## Feedback and Issues

Found a bug or have a suggestion? Feel free to [open an issue](https://github.com/MarcioMed07/Galaxy-Pong/issues) on GitHub. Your feedback is valuable!

